## Failure Handling

- Never block a response waiting for Honcho — all calls run after responding when possible.
- On any Honcho failure: continue conversation normally, note failure quietly.
- If MCP is down: run `./start.sh` from repo root to bring up the stack.
- If state file missing: call `setup_agent_workspace` to recreate it.
